The X Factor UK - Series 12, Episode 8




Boot Camp 1

The first of two boot-camp programmes sees the successful contestants from the arena auditions stage undertake a series of singing challenges when they are put through their paces by judges Simon Cowell, Cheryl Fernandez-Versini, Rita Ora and Nick Grimshaw at a grand country house. Presented by Caroline Flack and Olly Murs.




Original Air Date: 20-Sep-2015
